Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.79,0:00:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought the bus ticket for you in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.13,0:00:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is the option of giving yourself \N up, and then proving your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not pursuing Johan in order to prove my innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you aren't possibly thinking of...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't looking down on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you looked like an interesting guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't get a chance to get to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we've finally become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you saw me cheating...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was cheating too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that road sign just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having a little trouble with this map...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which way we're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get that map?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.68,0:01:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the car rental counter, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably while I was in the restroom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's of no use anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This map is too complicated for someone my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you forgot your reading glasses at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nippenhausen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anwertzhausen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gartelzhausen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What's up with all these unpronounceable names?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's it funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Germans think the \N same thing when they come to England.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, where is the next crossroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can ask them for directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're fine.  Let's just keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they are hitchhikers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if we get into trouble \N because we picked up God-knows who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a small boy with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel sorry for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we give them a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Tenma!  They stopped for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:39.00,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,96)\pos(356,312)}Journey to Freiham 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guten Tag.  Bitte...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't understand German.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you speak English?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you from England?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to get to Freiham.  Can we get a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place you want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're around here right now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,down south from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's in the same direction we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hop on, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Danke schön!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.17,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(347,297)\fad(150,71)}Bayern \N (Germany)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are your two related?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely not family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Asian,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he looks like he's German.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my friend's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from your looks, you're in some \N kind of specialized profession, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you talk, your mannerisms...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bad habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just can't get rid of his old habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to be a policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to be with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get off, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the two of you are taking a \N trip now that your husband has retired?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, in a manner of speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was such a hard worker,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it used to be impossible to take trips together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for interrupting your private vacation like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if we're too much trouble, we can--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.  We managed to rent a car at the \N airport, but we can't read the damn map.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having a hard time even ordering food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel better if someone were here to act as a translator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much we can do about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to go to a nearby gas station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!  There is a car coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be good, way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can take up to two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jones...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.  You two get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be concerned about us and stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll let people know that you are stuck here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we get to a gas station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got to switch cars just when we needed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop at a gas station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are very late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people at the gas station will come
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once that man tells them we are here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he just kept going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he was a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've mentioned the sunset many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it plenty of times, so I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, not the sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The color of the sky after the sun has set.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Robert is seeing this sky also.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?  I knew they would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They gave us some gas and a lamp at a nearby farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, translating the German menu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we had a great dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially that wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Forst Ungeheuer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wine from the Pfalz region.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.  And that dish with the liver, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leberknödel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, it was so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without you, we would have missed \N out on all the good food in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must thank you for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:12:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like another ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, he's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this guy did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about this man who is \N being charged with his wife's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may look old now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I was a detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a pretty good name for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start your stories here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be able to tell if a man was guilty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether he was a truly evil man \N or not, just by looking at his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you drank too much wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you do that for so long, you can't really tell anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good man and a bad man;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a criminal and an innocent;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you become unable to tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it just means I wasn't a great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did drink too much wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say it was called again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ungeheuer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, how cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if Dieter made some more \N friends at his new home, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has their own happy childhood, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but would you mind if we made a little stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two can just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what should we do, Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there is someone parked in a cruiser's spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it looked like they are foreigners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the opposite direction from Freiham,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is where we were headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't take too much of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to stop at Castle Steinbach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Castle Steinbach?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something I'd like to see first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our son's letter mentioned this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the view from the castle was spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he would like us to see it also.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then your son is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on our way to see him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we just keep making stops along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was looking at this view.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our son...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our son...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to this country to visit him in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll be leaving you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have our sincere gratitude as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a nice man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:21:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is wanted for multiple homicides.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, how can it be?  Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen him on the wanted list in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, when we went to see \N the detective who arrested Robert,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his picture was posted inside the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a good man...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was doubtful myself, when I first saw his picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I became certain when I met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He definitely is not an evil man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robert...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our son committed murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even see the signs within my own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized this, I quit being a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:22:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I want to have confidence in my own intuition again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robert committed a crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he is not evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's go see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robert.
